	"scenes":[
		{
			"title":"",
			"text":
				"Good job finding that Aegis prototype. The Emprire won't be happy about
				losing their prize weapon, so get back to Resistance territory as soon
				as possible. Our satellites show heavy enemy resistance blocking your escape.
				Prevent the Imperial forces from retaking that Aegis unit at all costs!"
		},
		{
			"title":"",
			"text":
				"Great work. We were able to destroy what was left of the weapons lab while
				you escaped. This Aegis unit may be just what we need. The Empire's moonbase superweapon has
				made it impossible to fight them directly. If you can take that out, we may have
				a chance. Unfortunately, Aegis is incapable of space flight. Head to the Empire's
				launch facility in the desert and commandeer a shuttle. Be careful, you're entering enemy territory."
		},
		{
			"title":"",
			"text":
				"Well done. You're at the outskirts of the base now.
				Our intel suggests a few patrols, but nothing that you can't handle."
		},
		{
			"title":"",
			"text":
				"You've made it inside the Imperial base. Force your way through, and find a shuttle!"
		}
	],
